{"title":"四川民谚","authors":[],"dates":[{"year":1957,"month":2,"day":9}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"四川民谚"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"姑娘怕误女婿、庄稼怕误节气。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"秀才不怕蓝衫破，只怕肚子没得货。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"灯盏不明有人拨，事情不平有人说。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"急水也有回头浪。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"独柴难烧，独儿难教。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刀钝石上磨，人笨人前学。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刀儿不磨要生锈，人不学习要落后。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"勤勤谨谨，衣衫齐整；懒懒惰惰，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挨饥受饿。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（犁　辑）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}